data.description:
Move in ready 3 bedroom, 1 bathroom home centrally located within 1.5 miles of Blinn College, downtown Bryan & St. Joseph Hospital. Additionally, Texas A&M University and the Health Science Center are within a minutes drive of the property, too!

This house has many upgrades including a concrete driveway, side gate, remote controlled ceiling fans, electrical panel, new plug outlets/coverings, tile in bathroom & laundry room. With the updated electrical work, you can run a freezer or even a welder in the 8' x 10' shop in the backyard. 

This charming home was built in 1949 and has a pier and beam foundation in the main living space. Originally built as a 2 bedroom/1 bathroom, the garage has been converted into a third bedroom which sits on a solid foundation. The house is all electric, no gas with W/D hookups and includes an electrical stove, microwave and fridge. The A/C unit & roof are both 6 years old (2017) and have recently been inspected. 

Enjoy a superb location, spacious backyard and the convenience of being a stones throw away from Sue Haswell Park. Please contact Elliot for more information at 979-450-1243.
